    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1868-04-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1868-04-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="377" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d377">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Señor Gomez</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-04-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 20, 1868.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have had the honor to receive your
                                note of the 16th, stating that on the 4th instant you had addressed
                                a note to the representatives of Peru, Spain, and Chili, offering
                                the good offices of the Central American states towards co-operating
                                either in the acceptance by the belligerents of the mediation which
                                has been offered by the United States for the purpose of putting an
                                end to the contest, or for bringing about by some other means an
                                agreement to open negotiations for peace.</p>
                <p>Your well-intentioned proceeding in this matter is approved by the
                                President, who hopes it may contribute to the result which is
                                earnestly desired by the government.</p>
                <p>I avail myself of this occasion to offer to you a renewed assurance
                                of my high consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Señor Don <hi rend="smallcaps">Ignacio Gomez</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
